    "heading_text": "Recap",
    "anchor_id": "recap",
    "section_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/dependencies/sub-dependencies/#recap",
    "section_text": "Apart from all the fancy words used here, the Dependency Injection system is quite simple.\n\nJust functions that look the same as the path operation functions .\n\nBut still, it is very powerful, and allows you to declare arbitrarily deeply nested dependency \"graphs\" (trees).",
    "section_inline_code": [],
